# The patch scripts and the runner execute via their shebang line. A CRLF ending
# turns `#!/usr/bin/python3` into `#!/usr/bin/python3\r`, which the loader cannot
# find (exit 127). Force LF on checkout regardless of the machine's core.autocrlf
# (Git for Windows defaults it to true, which would otherwise rewrite these to
# CRLF on clone and silently break every patch).
*.py  text eol=lf
*.sh  text eol=lf
